<br>
And, IMHO, the aggro advantages of a faster weapon for a paladin is  largely a myth. I am sure faster weapons aid warriors in holding aggro, but weapon speed and weapon procs are all they have (besides taunt). Paladins have many additional methods (primarily stuns) to hold aggro. I have never had a problem holding aggro with a two handed weapon. <p>Marlowe Lawbringer<BR>
